casebody.data:
Steven HULTQUIST and Debra Hultquist
v.
Dr. Leslie MORROW, Dr. Michael Lish and David Daniel Construction Company. No. 215P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 30, 2005. Steven Hultquist, Research Triangle Park, for Steven & Debra Hultquist. Nicholas P. Robinson, for Morrow, et al.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 20th day of April 2005 by Plaintiffs in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 30th day of June 2005."
